Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.62,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Give a synopsis of the last episode, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:07.39,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:12.50,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned to my hometown, Little Monica, after being away for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.00,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The changes I saw were staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:20.21,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone used to love the arts. Everyone used to be generous and happy in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:27.05,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, Kajo rules the city, and it is overrun with evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.86,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I restore Little Monica back to the cheerful city that it used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:38.36,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I have to think of the city now.
