Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.60,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The strip show you went to is one of the few places where it's allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.77,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only play our instruments because we're not in the center of the city, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.78,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have to be careful. If we get caught, we'll be sent to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.14,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because of Kajo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.45,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing we need to do is figure out how to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.48,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Kajo has enough money from his shady businesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.88,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bribe both the army and the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.95,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is too scared to speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.96,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.47,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:23.74,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too young when Mom left, so I don't really remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.81,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:25.31,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Will!
