Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:28.51,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.01,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Ingrid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:38.48,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you? This is Celia, Tina, and Mei. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.19,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.26,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any children. I've given myself to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:51.74,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you can tell I'm a nun by just looking at me. Are you making fun of me?
