Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:59.28,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the oldest, so my memory is the best. She's definitely Ingrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.71,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.82,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:28.60,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:33.37,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Celia, I'm sorry I've taken over a corner of your store.
