Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.32,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd better work hard to rebuild this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:56.03,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Will, I had a lot of fun yesterday. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:01.57,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,About our mother... You did your best for us, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.54,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that... I was raised by foster parents, and some things were hard...
