Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:20.49,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Will. It's the thought that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:26.53,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not have been her, but we'll have you from now on, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.77,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'll take good care of all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:39.01,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm really sure that woman is your mother, Ingrid.
