Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:46.55,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong, Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.99,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. I didn't even notice you come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.96,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you friends with Will?
