Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.86,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,She just surprised me because she said that suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.53,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:06.80,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a traveling fortune-teller. I heard that the coffee here is great, so I stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:11.61,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,When I overheard your interesting conversation, I listened in.
