Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:27.39,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me that she lost her memory, but she also said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.89,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...that there is something familiar about this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:37.33,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there is someone out there that is precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.17,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Will! Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:43.24,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be you girls! That woman is Ingrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.61,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go look for Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.31,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.78,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,She also said there is someone out there who wants to harm her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:59.12,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I can tell, this harm will also affect Little Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:04.72,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to listen, because this has to do with the fate of Little Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.56,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll still have time to look for your mother afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.13,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll listen. I'll get my sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:18.94,LM_Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my sisters, Tina and Mei. We're all here now.
